Below is the proprietary JSON template for the argument section:

```json
{
  "section_type": "argument",
  "structure": [
    {"heading": "Introduction", "elements": ["issue_statement", "summary_of_facts"]},
    {"heading": "Legal Standard", "elements": ["relevant_cases", "statutory_framework"]},
    {"heading": "Analysis", "elements": ["element_1", "element_2", "element_3"]},
    {"heading": "Conclusion", "elements": ["relief_requested"]}
  ],
  "style_guidelines": {
    "citation_format": "Bluebook",
    "sentence_length": "average",
    "voice": "active",
    "tone": "persuasive"
  }
}
```
